messages.message: I tried this query, but I don't think it's completely removing Instabase users. Here is the query result, where I can still see Instabase users like piyush.agrawal and puneet.rai.

Yeah, unfortunately there isn't another reliable internal/external flag. FWIW, I believe other metrics we use to split internal/external use that filter.

How do we plan to ultimately use this data?

@jack.robbins we want to be able to understand which apps are being looked at by folks and either improve them over time or create short videos to promote them. Additionally with the revamp of the marketplace and making them more searchable this would be a good metric to know how effective MP apps are and therefore how much we need to focus on them
